version             1.1.3
categories          x11
license             X11
maintainers         {jeremyhu @jeremyhu} openmaintainer
description         X11 clipboard client
long_description \
   The xclipboard program is used to collect and display text selections \
   that are sent to the CLIPBOARD by other clients.

